  <h2 class="helpHeader"> Having a problem?</h2> 
        <div class="helpText">
<p class="helpP1">Here is how it works step by step..<br /> <br />
1.	Once you are signed in, fill the form completely and click on the ‘Check Available Asset’ button. The result of your search will be displayed below the form.<br /><br />
2.	Choose the asset you would like to borrow by ticking the corresponding checkbox. You can choose to borrow more than one asset at a time.<br /> <br />
3.	Click on the confirm button to book the asset. Your booking is now complete. You will also receive a confirmation email shortly after. <br /><br />
</p>
</div>
<h2 class="helpHeader">So far so good…</h2>
<div class="helpText">
<p class="helpP1">You can do more here… <br /><br />
•	To view your current booking, click on the ’My Booking’ link on either the top right corner, or bottom middle of the page.<br /> <br />
•	To cancel your booking, simply tick the corresponding checkbox and click on ‘Cancel’ button. Please drop the IT team an email so they know, thanks. <br /><br />
•	The calendar will allow you to view all current booking. To do this, click on the ‘Calendar’ link and choose a date. If there is a booking for that date it will be displayed on the top part of the page. <br /><br />
</p>
</div>
<h2 class="helpHeader">This is why…</h2>
        <div class="helpText">
    <p class="helpP1">
•	IF you can’t see the search result, this is because the search table is displayed at the bottom of the form. Please scroll down after clicking on the ‘Check Available Asset’ button. <br /><br />
•	IF you can’t see the asset you are looking for, it might be because of your search criteria. Please change, or make sure you search criteria is correct. <br /><br />
•	IF you are unable to receive a confirmation email, it means our system can’t find your email address. You will be notified of this when booking. In this case, please contact the IT guys. <br /><br />
</p>
</div>
<h2 class="helpHeader">Please do…</h2>
        <div class="helpText">
    <p class="helpP1">
•	Click on ‘Check Available Asset’ button to update the search when changing search criteria <br /><br />
•	Send the IT team an email if you cancel a booking<br /><br />
•	Cancel booking if you don’t need the asset anymore<br /><br />
</p>
</div>
